<h3>Grading</h3>
<p>Course grades will be based 40% on homework, 5% on class participation, 15% + 15% on scheduled midterm quizzes, and 25% on the final exam.
</p>

<h3>Policy on collaboration</h3>
<p>We encourage students to collaborate on problem sets. However, the work you submit must reflect your own analysis of the problems and must not have been copied from the work of another student.
</p>

<h3>Exams</h3>
<p>Quizzes will be 10/8 and 11/12. Note that quizzes will be outside of regular class hours, on Tuesday evenings. There will also be a final at a date and time to be determined.
</p>

